sect1.para:
View>Go to Previous Buffer
(keyboard shortcut: ControlPage Up
) switches to the previous buffer in the list.

View>Go to Next Buffer
(keyboard shortcut: ControlPage Down
) switches to the next buffer in the list.

sidebar.para:
These commands cannot be invoked from the menu bar. However, they can be
added to the tool bar or context menu, and given keyboard shortcuts;
see .
